node.text: @playbasedlearningnyc Indeed! He is so pleased with his idea! 😍

We were reading a book and the last scene was of two children sleeping on a bunk bed. He stood up smiling and declared: Hugo wants to build a bed. Next he went into the room and pulled out a ‘bed’, pillow and blanket, hoisted it up the top bunk of his new bed 😄 His sense of joy and pride to see his idea come into life is priceless. #followingjoy #followthechild #letthemexplore #letthemplay #bunkbed #bunkbedsforkids #imaginaryplay #playpretend #imaginativeplay #homesweethome #stayhomesg #stayhomeforsg #sgunited
@ofupsanddowns Thank you! Its a privilege fun to follow the child’s mind! 😄
@starmaria75 Thank you my dear!! They inspire me everyday! ❤️❤️
Mama you are so inspiring to your kids !💕❤️❤️😊
@playbasedlearningnyc Indeed! He is so pleased with his idea! 😍
Doesn’t he look cute and cozy!
